long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unofficial tool for copying variable sets in Octopus Deploy (www.octopus.com). 
Tested on Octopus Versions 3.3.11 - 3.7.3
Version 0.2.0 Updates:
 - Added Https support.

*Try to backup your Octopus Deploy before copying variable sets
**Use this tool at your own risk. Copying variables without paying attention, can result in unexpected behavior with Octopus Deploy deployments.
